    "body": "Using the following config:\n\n```lua\nvim.pack.add {\n  'https://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig',\n}\nvim.diagnostic.config {\n  signs = false,\n}\nvim.lsp.enable('lua_ls')\n```\n\nWhen diagnostics are shown in the statusline by `vim.diagnostic.status()`, the following error is raised:\n\n```\nE5108: Lua: /home/liv/src/neovim//runtime/lua/vim/diagnostic.lua:1126: attempt to index field 'signs' (a boolean value)                                                                         \nstack traceback:                                                                                \n        /home/liv/src/neovim//runtime/lua/vim/diagnostic.lua:1126: in function 'status'         \n        [string \"luaeval()\"]:1: in main chunk  \n```\n\nIssue bisected to b56f7c6edd339ab8be32738f1ecb0d7056b7ab9c #39525 @ofseed ",
